ource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 2438, \"end\": 2444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999996368706638, \"rank\": 3.631293564858193e-07, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"TIAHURA\", \"from\": 2394, \"to\": 2401}, {\"ngram\": \"their days\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2434}, {\"ngram\": \"fishers\", \"from\": 2479, \"to\": 2486}, {\"ngram\": \"their catches\", \"from\": 2495, \"to\": 2508}, {\"ngram\": \"the fish\", \"from\": 2515, \"to\": 2523}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With fishing being a vital part of the ways of Polynesian life, local leader Dominique Tehei, 51, and his fellow community members knew they needed to find a way to restore the ecosystem.\", \"from\": 2556, \"to\": 2743, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2603, \"end\": 2613, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\", \"score\": 0.9898768311770657, \"rank\": 0.010138393207888879, \"text\": \"Polynesian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fishing\", \"from\": 2561, \"to\": 2568}, {\"ngram\": \"a vital part\", \"from\": 2575, \"to\": 2587}, {\"ngram\": \"the ways\", \"from\": 2591, \"to\": 2599}, {\"ngram\": \"local leader Dominique Tehei\", \"from\": 2620, \"to\": 2648}, {\"ngram\": \"his fellow community members\", \"from\": 2658, \"to\": 2686}, {\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 2712, \"to\": 2717}, {\"ngram\": \"the ecosystem\", \"from\": 2729, \"to\": 2742}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They decided there was a customary Polynesian practice that could help them do it: creating a rahui.\", \"from\": 2744, \"to\": 2844, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2779, \"end\": 2789, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\", \"score\": 0.98987683117