3083, \"to\": 3100}, {\"ngram\": \"leaders\", \"from\": 3105, \"to\": 3112}, {\"ngram\": \"rahui\", \"from\": 3130, \"to\": 3135}, {\"ngram\": \"a one-stop solution\", \"from\": 3144, \"to\": 3163}, {\"ngram\": \"all environmental issues\", \"from\": 3167, \"to\": 3191}, {\"ngram\": \"researchers\", \"from\": 3215, \"to\": 3226}, {\"ngram\": \"scientists\", \"from\": 3231, \"to\": 3241}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground-up\", \"from\": 3261, \"to\": 3274}, {\"ngram\": \", community-based approach\", \"from\": 3274, \"to\": 3300}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For centuries, rahui have been implemented in the French Polynesian islands, Hawaii and New Zealand, temporarily banning or restricting the harvesting of natural resources in designated areas, said Hunter Lenihan, an ecologist and co-director of the Rahui Forum and Resource Center headquartered in Moorea, Tahiti.\", \"from\": 3303, \"to\": 3617, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3353, \"end\": 3359, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.999379909469354, \"rank\": 0.0006160679841347344, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 3360, \"end\": 3370, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\", \"score\": 0.9898768311770657, \"rank\": 0.010138393207888879, \"text\": \"Polynesian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\"}, {\"begin\": 3380, \"end\": 3386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hawaii\", \"score\": 0.9999999888646017, \"rank\": 1.1135305031995405e-08, \"text\": \"Hawaii\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hawaii\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hawaii\"}, {\"begin\": 3391, \"end\": 3402, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealanders\", \"score\": 0.996913221022829, \"rank\": 0.003095037533220941, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealanders\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealanders\"}, {\"begin\": 3501, \"end\": 3507, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hunter_Region\", \"score\": 0.9973890849350637, \"rank\": 0.00260696635767615, \"text\": \"Hunter\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hunter_Region\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hunter_Region\"}, {\"begin\": 3610, \"end\": 3616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999996368706638, \"rank\": 3.631293564858193e-07, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"centuries\", \"from\": 3307, \"to\": 3316}, {\"ngram\": \"rahui\", \"from\": 3318, \"to\": 3323}, {\"ngram\": \"the harvesting\", \"from\": 3439, \"to\": 3453}, {\"ngram\": \"natural resources\", \"from\": 3457, \"to\": 3474}, {\"ngram\": \"designated areas\", \"from\": 3478, \"to\": 3494}, {\"ngram\": \"an ecologist and co-director\", \"from\": 3517, \"to\": 3545}, {\"ngram\": \"the Rahui Forum and Resource Center\", \"from\": 3549, \"to\": 3584}, {\"ngram\": \"Moorea\", \"from\": 3602, \"to\": 3608}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"(The practice) was squashed by colonizers,\\\" said Lenihan, \\\"but \\u2026 is going through a revival that began intensively about a decade ago.\\\"\", \"from\": 3619, \"to\": 3755, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The practice\", \"from\": 3621, \"to\": 3633}, {\"ngram\": \"colonizers\", \"from\": 3651, \"to\": 3661}, {\"ngram\": \"Lenihan\", \"from\": 3669, \"to\": 3676}, {\"ngram\": \"a revival\", \"from\": 3702, \"to\": 3711}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While the most common form of rahui is a no-fishing zone placed in a lagoon or offshore - like a marine reserve - rahui have also been established in local creeks and rivers in the form of planting taro crops to capture sediment from agriculture or other development before it flows into the ocean and harmfully settles onto reefs.\", \"from\": 3757, \"to\": 4088, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most common form\", \"from\": 3763, \"to\": 3783}, {\"ngram\": \"rahui\", \"from\": 3787, \"to\": 3792}, {\"ngram\": \"a no-fishing zone\", \"from\": 3796, \"to\": 3813}, {\"ngram\": \"a lagoon\", \"from\": 3824, \"to\": 3832}, {\"ngram\": \"a marine reserve - rahui\", \"from\": 3852, \"to\": 3876}, {\"ngram\": \"local creeks\", \"from\": 3907, \"to\": 3919}, {\"ngram\": \"rivers\", \"from\": 3924, \"to\": 3930}, {\"ngram\": \"the form\", \"from\": 3934, \"to\": 3942}, {\"ngram\": \"planting taro crops\", \"from\": 3946, \"to\": 3965}, {\"ngram\": \"sediment\", \"from\": 3977, \"to\": 3985}, {\"ngram\": \"agriculture\", \"from\": 3991, \"to\": 4002}, {\"ngram\": \"other development\", \"from\": 4006, \"to\": 4023}, {\"ngram\": \"the ocean\", \"from\": 4045, \"to\": 4054}, {\"ngram\": \"reefs\", \"from\": 4082, \"to\": 4087}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even in the no-fishing zones, rules can vary based on the area's needs.\", \"from\": 4090, \"to\": 4161, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the no-fishing zones\", \"from\": 4098, \"to\": 4118}, {\"ngram\": \"rules\", \"from\": 4120, \"to\": 4125}, {\"ngram\": \"the area's needs\", \"from\": 4144, \"to\": 4160}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes, fishing is only permitted during a certain season.\", \"from\": 4162, \"to\": 4223, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fishing\", \"from\": 4173, \"to\": 4180}, {\"ngram\": \"a certain season\", \"from\": 4206, \"to\": 4222}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Other times, only certain methods like line or spear fishing are permitted, forbidding the use of nets or cages.\", \"from\": 4224, \"to\": 4336, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"only certain methods\", \"from\": 4237, \"to\": 4257}, {\"ngram\": \"line\", \"from\": 4263, \"to\": 4267}, {\"ngram\": \"spear fishing\", \"from\": 4271, \"to\": 4284}, {\"ngram\": \"the use\", \"from\": 4311, \"to\": 4318}, {\"ngram\": \"nets\", \"from\": 4322, \"to\": 4326}, {\"ngram\": \"cages\", \"from\": 4330, \"to\": 4335}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In some rahui, fishing and swimming is prohibited entirely, protecting some areas from tourism overdevelopment.\", \"from\": 4337, \"to\": 4448, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some rahui\", \"from\": 4340, \"to\": 4350}, {\"ngram\": \"fishing\", \"from\": 4352, \"to\": 4359}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 4364, \"to\": 4372}, {\"ngram\": \"some areas\", \"from\": 4408, \"to\": 4418}, {\"ngram\": \"tourism overdevelopment\", \"from\": 4424, \"to\": 4447}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Decisions on where, how and when to establish a rahui are made and managed by community leaders.\", \"from\": 4450, \"to\": 4546, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Decisions\", \"from\": 4450, \"to\": 4459}, {\"ngram\": \"a rahui\", \"from\": 4496, \"to\": 4503}, {\"ngram\": \"community leaders\", \"from\": 4528, \"to\": 4545}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the years leading up to the 2019 establishment of the rahui in Teva I Uta, where Tehei lives, Tehei said he and other conservationists initially had a hard time convincing villagers that a rahui would be a good idea.\", \"from\": 4548, \"to\": 4767, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4614, \"end\": 4624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Teva_I_Uta\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Teva I Uta\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Teva_I_Uta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Teva_I_Uta\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the years\", \"from\": 4551, \"to\": 4560}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2019 establishment\", \"from\": 4575, \"to\": 4597}, {\"ngram\": \"the rahui\", \"from\": 4601, \"to\": 4610}, {\"ngram\": \"Tehei\", \"from\": 4632, \"to\": 4637}, {\"ngram\": \"Tehei\", \"from\": 4645, \"to\": 4650}, {\"ngram\": \"other conservationists\", \"from\": 4663, \"to\": 4685}, {\"ngram\": \"a hard time\", \"from\": 4700, \"to\": 4711}, {\"ngram\": \"villagers\", \"from\": 4723, \"to\": 4732}, {\"ngram\": \"a rahui\", \"from\": 4738, \"to\": 4745}, {\"ngram\": \"a good idea\", \"from\": 4755, \"to\": 4766}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Fishing is what provides resource money and food,\\\" said Tehei.\", \"from\": 4769, \"to\": 4832, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Fishing\", \"from\": 4770, \"to\": 4777}, {\"ngram\": \"resource money\", \"from\": 4795, \"to\": 4809}, {\"ngram\": \"food\", \"from\": 4814, \"to\": 4818}, {\"ngram\": \"Tehei\", \"from\": 4826, \"to\": 4831}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They were afraid of not being able to access it when they were in the most need.\", \"from\": 4833, \"to\": 4914, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most need\", \"from\": 4900, \"to\": 4913}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So of course they were a little nervous about that.\\\"\", \"from\": 4915, \"to\": 4967, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 4921, \"to\": 4927}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Going home to home, Tehei said they were able to convince villagers to allow certain sections of the reef and surrounding areas to be closed for two years at a time, leaving other sections still open for fishing activities.\", \"from\": 4969, \"to\": 5192, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 4983, \"to\": 4987}, {\"ngram\": \"Tehei\", \"from\": 4989, \"to\": 4994}, {\"ngram\": \"villagers\", \"from\": 5027, \"to\": 5036}, {\"ngram\": \"certain sections\", \"from\": 5046, \"to\": 5062}, {\"ngram\": \"the reef\", \"from\": 5066, \"to\": 5074}, {\"ngram\": \"surrounding areas\", \"from\": 5079, \"to\": 5096}, {\"ngram\": \"two years\", \"from\": 5114, \"to\": 5123}, {\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 5127, \"to\": 5133}, {\"ngram\": \"other sections\", \"from\": 5143, \"to\": 5157}, {\"ngram\": \"fishing activities\", \"from\": 5173, \"to\": 5191}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tehei has not been alone in his advocacy efforts for establishing rahui across Tahiti.\", \"from\": 5194, \"to\": 5280, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5273, \"end\": 5279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999996368706638, \"rank\": 3.631293564858193e-07, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tehei\", \"from\": 5194, \"to\": 5199}, {\"ngram\": \"his advocacy efforts\", \"from\": 5222, \"to\": 5242}, {\"ngram\": \"rahui\", \"from\": 5260, \"to\": 5265}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Members from the Rahui Forum and Resource Center visit and discuss with communities across Tahiti to help learn why they want to establish a rahui, then connect them with local nongovernmental organizations and community leaders who can help with the establishment process.\", \"from\": 5282, \"to\": 5555, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5373, \"end\": 5379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999996368706638, \"rank\": 3.631293564858193e-07, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Members\", \"from\": 5282, \"to\": 5289}, {\"ngram\": \"communities\", \"from\": 5354, \"to\": 5365}, {\"ngram\": \"a rahui\", \"from\": 5421, \"to\": 5428}, {\"ngram\": \"local nongovernmental organizations\", \"from\": 5453, \"to\": 5488}, {\"ngram\": \"community leaders\", \"from\": 5493, \"to\": 5510}, {\"ngram\": \"the establishment process\", \"from\": 5529, \"to\": 5554}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The system is built from ground up,\\\" said Lenihan.\", \"from\": 5557, \"to\": 5608, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The system\", \"from\": 5558, \"to\": 5568}, {\"ngram\": \"ground\", \"from\": 5583, \"to\": 5589}, {\"ngram\": \"Lenihan\", \"from\": 5600, \"to\": 5607}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Community leaders and government officials have also led information campaigns, with billboards and posters about rahui being posted across church, schools and town halls across Tahiti.\", \"from\": 5610, \"to\": 5795, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5788, \"end\": 5794, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999996368706638, \"rank\": 3.631293564858193e-07, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Community leaders\", \"from\": 5610, \"to\": 5627}, {\"ngram\": \"government officials\", \"from\": 5632, \"to\": 5652}, {\"ngram\": \"information campaigns\", \"from\": 5667, \"to\": 5688}, {\"ngram\": \"billboards\", \"from\": 5695, \"to\": 5705}, {\"ngram\": \"posters\", \"from\": 5710, \"to\": 5717}, {\"ngram\": \"church\", \"from\": 5750, \"to\": 5756}, {\"ngram\": \"schools\", \"from\": 5758, \"to\": 5765}, {\"ngram\": \"town halls\", \"from\": 5770, \"to\": 5780}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are now dozens of rahui across Tahiti, including in Teahupo'o, where surfers went head-to-head in the Paris Olympics surfing competition.\", \"from\": 5797, \"to\": 5940, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5834, \"end\": 5840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999996368706638, \"rank\": 3.631293564858193e-07, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}, {\"begin\": 5905, \"end\": 5919, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"dozens\", \"from\": 5811, \"to\": 5817}, {\"ngram\": \"rahui\", \"from\": 5821, \"to\": 5826}, {\"ngram\": \"Teahupo'o\", \"from\": 5855, \"to\": 5864}, {\"ngram\": \"surfers\", \"from\": 5872, \"to\": 5879}, {\"ngram\": \"head\", \"from\": 5893, \"to\": 5897}, {\"ngram\": \"surfing competition\", \"from\": 5920, \"to\": 5939}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Signs mark their presence, informing visitors of regulations and penalties for violating them.\", \"from\": 5942, \"to\": 6036, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Signs\", \"from\": 5942, \"to\": 5947}, {\"ngram\": \"their presence\", \"from\": 5953, \"to\": 5967}, {\"ngram\": \"visitors\", \"from\": 5979, \"to\": 5987}, {\"ngram\": \"regulations\", \"from\": 5991, \"to\": 6002}, {\"ngram\": \"penalties\", \"from\": 6007, \"to\": 6016}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Locals relaxing on the beach or working in tourism can point out buoys in the water marking the rahui zones while explaining how important they are for the community's conservation efforts.\", \"from\": 6037, \"to\": 6226, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Locals\", \"from\": 6037, \"to\": 6043}, {\"ngram\": \"the beach\", \"from\": 6056, \"to\": 6065}, {\"ngram\": \"tourism\", \"from\": 6080, \"to\": 6087}, {\"ngram\": \"buoys\", \"from\": 6102, \"to\": 6107}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 6111, \"to\": 6120}, {\"ngram\": \"the rahui zones\", \"from\": 6129, \"to\": 6144}, {\"ngram\": \"the community's conservation efforts\", \"from\": 6189, \"to\": 6225}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Acceptance of rahui has blossomed as well: A 2019 study by the Pew Bertarelli Ocean Legacy Project found that 90% of inhabitants in French Polynesia support rahui, much higher than the support for other legal conservation methods like protected marine areas.\", \"from\": 6228, \"to\": 6486, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Acceptance\", \"from\": 6228, \"to\": 6238}, {\"ngram\": \"rahui\", \"from\": 6242, \"to\": 6247}, {\"ngram\": \"A 2019 study\", \"from\": 6271, \"to\": 6283}, {\"ngram\": \"the Pew Bertarelli Ocean Legacy Project\", \"from\": 6287, \"to\": 6326}, {\"ngram\": \"90%\", \"from\": 6338, \"to\": 6341}, {\"ngram\": \"inhabitants\", \"from\": 6345, \"to\": 6356}, {\"ngram\": \"French Polynesia\", \"from\": 6360, \"to\": 6376}, {\"ngram\": \"the support\", \"from\": 6409, \"to\": 6420}, {\"ngram\": \"other legal conservation methods\", \"from\": 6425, \"to\": 6457}, {\"ngram\": \"protected marine areas\", \"from\": 6463, \"to\": 6485}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rahui have been legally recognized in the French Polynesia environmental code since 2016.\", \"from\": 6487, \"to\": 6576, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Rahui\", \"from\": 6487, \"to\": 6492}, {\"ngram\": \"the French Polynesia environmental code\", \"from\": 6525, \"to\": 6564}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Tehei acknowledged the rahui system is not perfect: Sometimes, it's hard to monitor the entire area, especially during new moons when it's darker outside.\", \"from\": 6578, \"to\": 6736, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tehei\", \"from\": 6582, \"to\": 6587}, {\"ngram\": \"the rahui system\", \"from\": 6601, \"to\": 6617}, {\"ngram\": \"the entire area\", \"from\": 6666, \"to\": 6681}, {\"ngram\": \"new moons\", \"from\": 6701, \"to\": 6710}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Other times, they have had to open a rahui before the ecosystem had a chance to fully recover, as part of their timeline promises to fishers.\", \"from\": 6737, \"to\": 6878, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a rahui\", \"from\": 6772, \"to\": 6779}, {\"ngram\": \"the ecosystem\", \"from\": 6787, \"to\": 6800}, {\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 6805, \"to\": 6813}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 6835, \"to\": 6839}, {\"ngram\": \"their timeline promises\", \"from\": 6843, \"to\": 6866}, {\"ngram\": \"fishers\", \"from\": 6870, \"to\": 6877}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A lack of management during the opening of one rahui led to overfishing, he said.\", \"from\": 6879, \"to\": 6960, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"management\", \"from\": 6889, \"to\": 6899}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening\", \"from\": 6907, \"to\": 6918}, {\"ngram\": \"one rahui\", \"from\": 6922, \"to\": 6931}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We did not have an eye on who was going on the reef and unfortunately I would say within three weeks after the reopening \\u2026 the whole island came.\", \"from\": 6962, \"to\": 7108, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an eye\", \"from\": 6979, \"to\": 6985}, {\"ngram\": \"the reef\", \"from\": 7006, \"to\": 7014}, {\"ngram\": \"three weeks\", \"from\": 7052, \"to\": 7063}, {\"ngram\": \"the reopening\", \"from\": 7070, \"to\": 7083}, {\"ngram\": \"the whole island\", \"from\": 7086, \"to\": 7102}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We had 30 boats fishing,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 7109, \"to\": 7143, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"30 boats\", \"from\": 7116, \"to\": 7124}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was a total disaster.\\\"\", \"from\": 7144, \"to\": 7170, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a total disaster\", \"from\": 7152, \"to\": 7168}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tehei said despite the setbacks, they are still continuing to promote and monitor different ways to improve their rahui practices, including working with the local government to help create a fishing registration system that would catalog how much each fisher catches.\", \"from\": 7172, \"to\": 7440, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tehei\", \"from\": 7172, \"to\": 7177}, {\"ngram\": \"the setbacks\", \"from\": 7191, \"to\": 7203}, {\"ngram\": \"different ways\", \"from\": 7254, \"to\": 7268}, {\"ngram\": \"their rahui practices\", \"from\": 7280, \"to\": 7301}, {\"ngram\": \"the local government\", \"from\": 7326, \"to\": 7346}, {\"ngram\": \"a fishing registration system\", \"from\": 7362, \"to\": 7391}, {\"ngram\": \"how much each fisher catches\", \"from\": 7411, \"to\": 7439}]}